Useful for monitoring long-running DNS modifications and troubleshooting failed operations.
data.reasoning: Missing summary. Description lacks context about what Operations are, what the operation parameter represents, and what information is returned. Added clarity about operation ID parameter, status details including error information, and use case for monitoring and troubleshooting for better AI agent interpretability.
